    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Hi there, thanks for reaching out. \r\nYou should be able to achieve this with initialUiState.\r\nRoughly, for the price attribute:\r\n \r\n```js\r\nconst search = instantsearch({\r\n  indexName: 'my_index',\r\n  initialUiState: {\r\n    my_index: {\r\n      range: {\r\n        price: '200:400',\r\n      },\r\n    },\r\n  },\r\n});\r\n```\r\n\r\nHere is an example: https://codesandbox.io/s/affectionate-colden-cj7k9?file=/src/app.js:42-292\r\nI hope it helps!",
